---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Brand Repositioning Campaign" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">üé• Brand Repositioning Campaign</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <span class="badge badge-primary mr-2">Marketing</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Brand Strategy</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Stakeholder Management</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Content Creation</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <img src="/project3.webp" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-xl mb-6" alt="Brand Repositioning Campaign" />
    
    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>
      As a marketing intern, I was embedded in a team collaborating with an external agency on a company-wide rebranding campaign. 
      The initiative aimed to revitalize brand recognition and connect with a younger demographic through a promotional video campaign.
    </p>

    <h2>Role & Responsibilities</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-4">
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Strategic Bridge</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Connected internal stakeholders with creative team</li>
            <li>Facilitated feedback loops across departments</li>
            <li>Ensured alignment with brand messaging</li>
            <li>Coordinated review processes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Creative Input</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Reviewed and iterated on storyboards</li>
            <li>Suggested narrative simplifications</li>
            <li>Enhanced visual relatability</li>
            <li>Integrated user perception insights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Campaign Development Process</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <h3>Research & Planning</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Analyzed target demographic preferences</li>
          <li>Studied current brand perception</li>
          <li>Identified key messaging points</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <h3>Creative Development</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Collaborated on storyboard creation</li>
          <li>Refined visual elements</li>
          <li>Aligned with brand guidelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <h3>Implementation</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Coordinated multi-platform launch</li>
          <li>Managed stakeholder communications</li>
          <li>Monitored initial response</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Results & Impact</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-4">
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Video Views</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-primary">50K+</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Across platforms</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Brand Recall</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-secondary">+35%</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Post-campaign survey</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Target Audience</div>
          <div class="stat-value">‚ÜóÔ∏é</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Increased engagement</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Key Learnings</h2>
    <p>
      This experience provided valuable insights into:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cross-functional collaboration in creative projects</li>
      <li>Integration of customer insights into content strategy</li>
      <li>Effective storytelling for brand positioning</li>
      <li>Managing stakeholder expectations and feedback</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">‚Üê Back to Projects</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout> 